Tool Description Short: Nexis Uni is an affiliate database to LexisNexis and contains select databases found in Lexis, including over 15,000 news and business sources.

PitchBook is a financial data platform used by university libraries to provide detailed information on venture capital, private equity, and merger and acquisition activity across the private and public markets.

ProQuest (now a part of Clarivate) is a global information-content and technology company that provides academic libraries and researchers with access to a massive collection of digitized dissertations, historical newspapers, scholarly journals, and primary source documents.
The comprehensive flagship platform for business articles, though many institutions still pay for individual databases that feed into this aggregator.
